high_descs: Turn around and walk to the door then turn right and walk to the garbage.
Pick up the bar of soap that's in the garbage.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Get the bar of soap wet in the sink then get it back out after you close the faucet.
Open the cabinet door all the way to the left and put the soap in there and then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet bar of soap in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the garbage bin in the corner of the room.
Pick up the bar of soap from the garbage bin.
Turn right and walk forward to the sink on the left.
Put the bar of soap in the left sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Move slightly backwards away from the sink.
Open the bottom left cabinet below the sink on the left and put the bar of soap in it, in front of the purple cloth rag, then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned bar of soap in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and go right to face the trash can in the corner.
Pick the soap up out of the trash can.
Go right and face the sink on the left.
Put the soap in the sink on the left and turn on the water and then turn it off and pick up the soap.
Back up and turn to face the cabinet on the far left under the sinks.
Put the soap in the cabinet on the far left.
anns.task_desc: Put a bar of soap in a cabinet.
